headline: City of Centennial, Colorado, Renews Jacobs' Contract for Critical Infrastructure Services
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) was awarded a 15-year contract renewal from the City of Centennial, Colorado, to continue delivering vital public works services that enhance safety and livability for more than 110,000 residents.
